:: RUSTYCRYPTOVERSE ::
# 2 RustyCrypto WICK  

RustyWick and his trusty friend are relentless in the gang war that seeks to control the illegal distribution of Greenfluid. The symbiosis with the machines has given a new light of hope among those who still survive.

Collection: RustyCryptoVerse 

The RustyCryptoVerse is a collection of 101 rust-punk characters, randomly created with the aura of classic pop culture references from the last days on Earth, who are fighting on the epic search of the dominion and understanding of the Mysterious Greenfluid.
